list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: a complicated irregular network of passages or paths in which it is difficult to find one's way; a maze.
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: a labyrinth of passages and secret chambers
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: một mê cung của các đoạn và buồng bí mật

list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: a complex structure in the inner ear which contains the organs of hearing and balance. It consists of bony cavities (the bony labyrinth ) filled with fluid and lined with sensitive membranes (the membranous labyrinth ).
